Requires libglib2.0-dev, ctags, openssl, cmake, libwebsockets4.4.0, npm

on debian-

apt-get install libglib2.0-dev exuberant-ctags openssl cmake npm


To build type `make`.

Then "make install"- but there's no systemd/sysv startup script yet.

"make certs" to make some self signed ones.

"make systemd" to make locid run as lociterm.service

Edit the locid.conf config file per the comments.


To add proxy rules to apache2:
    RewriteEngine on
    RewriteCond %{HTTP:Upgrade} websocket [NC]
    RewriteCond %{HTTP:Connection} upgrade [NC]
    RewriteRule .* "wss://localhost:4005%{REQUEST_URI}" [P]
    ProxyPass /lociterm https://localhost:4005/
    ProxyPassReverse /lociterm https:///localhost:4005/
    ProxyRequests off

